Arch Boot Process
POST --> MBR(GRUB) --> /boot/kernel26.img --> initramfs --> /sbin/init -->
/etc/inittab 启动级别3
rc::sysinit:/etc/rc.sysinit
rs:S1:wait:/etc/rc.single
rm:2345:wait:/etc/rc.multi
sh:06:wait:/etc/rc.shutdown
su:S:wait:/sbin/sulogin
